112f51a0601414698fc8b033bf7d1256aededfe2d6518353b68cafd4f0294764bea21654104a3752d6d1ea0199400b27792d27d008c0cfef880f19ab08d9cfaf  config-oneplus-hotdog-lineage414.aarch64
02abe0a57020cf4a5ef6b8b8dd11be584ab7d4ceb7f1b010ce67728bd5675d9a2b3edc0e76ae2ac6f23c4ccdff77a6e02d94f3ce3560cf58cb7e47e30b0a138c  stock-hotdog-dtbpack.dtb
"
